THE GAME
--------

  'Pyramid' is a game where the goal is to find Pharaoh's tomb,
which is located at the topmost level in the pyramid. To get to
the tomb, you must move in a maze of corridors and ladders that
you have to climb up or down.

  To complicate matters, only a small portion (a 5 by 5 tile area)
of the pyramid is shown.

  You can move using the mouse or with the cursor keys of the
keyboard.

  Have fun!

